<div class="nbunit" id="31May1932"><font color="red">31 May 1932</font> <i>NLPK</i> (from Paul L&eacute;on to J. Ralph Pinker): He has also received a letter from Miss Sara Allgood, the actress, with a view to a public recitation or reading of <i>Anna Livia Plurabelle</i> by her at some London theatre </div>
